Package: blastar
Type: Package
Title: BLAST-Based Sequence Alignment and Tree Reconstruction
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Functions to align DNA sequences using BLAST, retrieve sequence data 
    from NCBI using rentrez, and construct neighbor-joining phylogenetic trees.
